Description_lang: Fatescribe Roh-Kalo rearranges the Loom of Fates, authoring for himself a glorious new fate. While he is doing so, his damage taken is reduced by $357739s1%.Several players are revealed as having Runic Affinity for the Loom's current configuration, and are capable of manipulating the position of the Loom's rings.After $s1 sec, if the rings are not returned to their target positions, Fatescribe Roh-Kalo invokes the Darkest Destiny, killing all players.
